name: stack
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "1.9.3" %}
{% set unixsha256 = "e2363728e5818ccc68db9371c15af892a9a1fc86d808d0a9a77257f13696e946" %}
{% set osxsha256 = "05ff745b88fb24911aa6b7e2b2e7098f04c2fdf769f00f921d44ffecbc417bc2" %}
{% set winsha256 = "9ff25247ad90478bdea042df2520e7865521d9023ba8dc6eae79875e1b11fcbb" %}

package:
  name: stack
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  fn: stack-{{ version }}-linux-x86_64.tar.gz  # [unix]
  url: https://github.com/commercialhaskell/stack/releases/download/v{{ version }}/stack-{{ version }}-linux-x86_64.tar.gz  # [unix]
  sha256: {{ unixsha256 }}  # [unix]
  fn: stack-{{ version }}-osx-x86_64.tar.gz  # [osx]
  url: https://github.com/commercialhaskell/stack/releases/download/v{{ version }}/stack-{{ version }}-osx-x86_64.tar.gz  # [osx]
  sha256: {{ osxsha256 }}  # [osx]
  fn: stack-{{ version }}-windows-x86_64.zip  # [win]
  url: https://github.com/commercialhaskell/stack/releases/download/v{{ version }}/stack-{{ version }}-windows-x86_64.zip  # [win]
  sha256: {{ winsha256 }}  # [win]

build:
  number: 1000

requirements:
  host:
    - gmp  # [not win]
  run:
    - gmp  # [not win]

test:
  commands:
    - stack --help
    - stack new helloworld new-template && cd helloworld && stack setup && stack build

about:
  home: www.haskellstack.org
  license: BSD3-like
  license_file: LICENSE
  summary: 'Stack is a cross-platform program for developing Haskell projects.'
  doc_url: https://docs.haskellstack.org/en/stable/README/
  dev_url: https://github.com/commercialhaskell/stack

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - eggzilla
